<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<title></title>
		<script src="js/mui.min.js"></script>
		<link href="css/mui.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/all.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/playvideo_all.css" />
		<style type="text/css">
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div class="mui-content">
			<img id="img-bg" src="img/material/video2.jpg" usemap="#map" />
			<map name="map" id="map">
				<area alt="area1" shape="rect" coords="650,1630,930,2120" href="index.html" />
			</map>
			<video id="video" src='raw/video/video2.mp4' poster="img/material/video2_1.png" controls="controls">
			</video>
			<div id="introduction">
				&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;过洋牵星术是郑和船队所用的天文观察导航技术。是指用牵星板测量所在地的星辰高度，然后计算出该处的地理纬度，以此测定船只的具体航向。牵星板是测量星体距水平线高度的仪器，其原理相当于当今的六分仪。通过牵星板测量星体高度，可以找到船舶在海上的位置。
				<br />
				<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;明代过洋牵星术常用的星座包括北辰星、织女星、布司星、牛郎星、南门双星、灯笼骨星等。

			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
	<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
		mui.init();
		mui.ready(function() {
			document.getElementsByClassName("mui-content")[0].style.height = innerHeight + "px";
			document.getElementsByClassName("mui-content")[0].style.width = innerWidth + "px";
			document.getElementById("video").addEventListener('ended', function(event) {
				this.load();
				this.play();
			});
			setTimeout(function() {
				location = 'index.html'
			}, 600000); //长时间无操作退回主页
		});
	</script>

</html>